TROLL

Trolls are massive, brutish humanoids with extraordinary physical power and
endurance.  On Rifts Earth they are often found as enforcers, heavy laborers,
and front-line soldiers in various armies.  Their low intelligence limits
their OCC options but their sheer physical capability makes them feared in
close combat.

ATTRIBUTES (approximate ranges):
  IQ: 3-13   ME: 2-12   MA: 2-12   PS: 14-34 (exceptional)
  PP: 2-12   PE: 10-30  PB: 1-6    Spd: 5-20

DAMAGE POOL:
  SDC: 3d6 x10 (approx 30-180)

SPECIAL ABILITIES:
  - Exceptional PS and PE: among the highest of OCC-eligible races
  - Massive natural resilience
  - Large physical presence

PENALTIES:
  - Low IQ, ME, MA, PP, and PB
  - Limited OCC access due to intelligence requirements
  - Intimidating appearance; distrusted in many communities
  - Cannot use standard human-sized equipment effectively

OCC ELIGIBLE: Yes (physical/combat OCCs only).
ALIGNMENT: Any.

See also: ogre, orc, goblin, occs, races
